                <text type="uv_alert">Sun protection 9:40am to 2:30pm, UV Index predicted to reach 5 [Moderate]</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="2" start-time-local="2026-04-21T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-04-22T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-04-20T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-04-21T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Mostly sunny. The chance of fog in the early morning, mainly in the west. Light winds becoming northerly 15 to 20 km/h in the middle of the day then tending northeasterly in the late afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to around 9 with daytime temperatures reaching the low 30s.</text>
